
## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# R
.Rhistory
.Rapp.history
.RData
.Ruserdata
.Rproj.user/

# RStudio project files
*.Rproj

# Quarto / R Markdown intermediates
*.html
*.utf8.md
*.knit.md
*_cache/
*_files/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Python / misc virtual envs
.venv/
venv/
env/

# Logs
*.log

# Local secrets / config
Renviron.site
.Renviron
.env
.env.*

# Data
data/raw/*
!data/raw/.gitkeep

# Processed outputs
data/processed/*
!data/processed/.gitkeep
!data/processed/tables/
!data/processed/figures/
data/processed/tables/manuscript/*
!data/processed/tables/manuscript/.gitkeep
data/processed/figures/manuscript/*
!data/processed/figures/manuscript/.gitkeep

# Large model/data artifacts
*.rds
*.rda
*.RDS
*.qs
*.fst
*.feather
*.parquet

# App runtime / deployment clutter
rsconnect/
shinyapps/

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.bak
*.swp
